response.about: Ни один из трех разновидностей Овнов не терпит скуки. Все они прирожденные весельчаки, очень любопытны и любят своих друзей. Любопытство иногда может сделать Овнов нетактичными, но не стоит обижаться на них всерьез: они никогда не хотят ничего дурного, а просто стремятся получше узнать жизнь во всех ее проявлениях. Ни с одним из Овнов лучше не пытаться спорить. Вам все равно не удастся переубедить этих яростных упрямцев и склонить их на свою сторону. Овнов крайне трудно заставить изменить свое мнение, которое они всегда считают истиной в последней инстанции. Овнам следует научиться сдерживать свои порывы, иначе несдержанность может довести их до склонности к агрессии и разрушению. Причем, в первую очередь, Овен постарается разрушить самое дорогое, что у него есть - себя самого.

response.about:
Korsakov-RED was born in Leningrad in 1986.
Musical career Korsakov-RED began when he was 5 years old. The first musical instrument was the violin. But the violin he played not long. At the age of 7 years Korsakov-RED starting school named after D. Shostakovich piano.
At that time there were his first musical compositions for piano. Parallel to the study of piano at the age of 14
Korsakov-RED entered the school of arts Rostropovich on trumpet. In 2003, the Korsakov-RED successfully completed
training on the trumpet and piano. Since 1996, the Korsakov-RED started to get involved in electronic music.

In the spring of 2007. Korsakov-RED began his career as a DJ in the School of Mix Master. At that time in the clubs of Saint Petersburg predominant electro house music. Korsakov-RED excellent acts in clubs "Barhat", "Griboyedov", "Beat Street", "Heat", "Anichkov Most", "Oxford", "DJ Bar Journalist".

But the monotonous house music quickly tired of him, and the fall of 2007, the light appears a musical project GET-Project. GET-Good Evening Trance. So called Trance evenings which take place every Monday Korsakov-RED and DJ Vivaldi in the "DJ Bar Journalist".

In spring 2008 the GET-project begins a series of night events trance music "Captivating Colours" in St. Petersburg. The first event Captivating Colours: "Dark blue" was held on May 30, 2008, which marked the beginning of a new promotional movement trance music in St. Petersburg.

In autumn 2008 the GET-Project extended the promotional group. And on Jan. 31, 2009 Captivating Colours opened the first trance event in 2009 in St. Petersburg. It was a "Launch on" @ Clubio. This event has become a new stage of trance music in the club life of St. Petersburg.

 

And the next step Captivating Colours were three events in autumn 2009 in the Club "Royal Beach", the guests have been known worldwide artists: Ronski Speed (GER), Cressida (GER), Sebastian Sand (PL), Claudia Cazacu (GB), Sophie Sugar (GB), Melodica (RU), Sonar (RU).

Now in the Captivating Colours include: dj Vivaldi (RU), Korsakov-RED (RU), Dash A (RU), Annie Glam (RU), Maretti (RU), Miki Lain (RU).

In spring 2010 Captivating Colours has launched its own internet radio "Captivating Colours Radio".
04/06/2010 was an acquaintance with the residents internet radio Captivating Colours with a live broadcast from a bar Gaspar internet radio broadcast.

Since 2007, the events Captivating Colours played more than 30 artists from different points of the planet.
